  "A straight line sloping upward from zero": "",
  "A flat horizontal line at 100 m/s": "",
  "A curved line bending downward sharply": "",
  "A straight line sloping downward to zero": "",
  "Uniform (constant) acceleration produces a straight line on a v-t graph. Since the rocket goes from 0 to 100 m/s, the line starts at the origin and slopes upward at a constant rate.": "",
