  "The car slowed, stopped, and reversed direction": "",
  "The car maintained a constant velocity": "",
  "The car remained completely stationary": "",
  "Going from +10 m/s to -10 m/s means the car was moving forward, slowed to zero (stopped momentarily), and then began moving backward. The sign change indicates a reversal of direction.": "",
